{"tid":1589743,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"以武制暴嘅人同我全部入曬黎 你地禁做係唔岩嫁","createTime":"2019-09-23T11:54:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-28T05:10:05.000Z","uid":71335,"like":32,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"78cf77feeccedbe261974d647e99b33102952624","tid":1589743,"uid":71335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T11:54:51.000Z","msg":"你地反擊完要等埋記者採訪佢地 個時要大叫<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">佢地追住人打 我地行使公民權利</span></span><br />\n<br />\n而家條條新聞片都淨係影到你地打佢 採訪又淨係得佢地講野 搞到新聞話你地無差別攻擊 比機會佢地發圍禁做係唔岩嫁<br />\n<br />\n下次記得行使完公民權要大叫呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9371393bbdd62c324b8f5903953d7c773f9a897e","tid":1589743,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T11:55:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1587564\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1587564</a>"},{"pid":"d1193828982b48e3b72418adc35c318542727708","tid":1589743,"uid":283781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T11:55:19.000Z","msg":"[緊急][公投][置頂] 10.1集合定分區搞<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1589182\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1589182</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"74df19f8b3ddac0e51d5853597a54e0572142b35","tid":1589743,"uid":71335,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T11:56:26.000Z","msg":"呀～ 條仆街追住人打 我地為左制服佢先用武力<br />\n唔洗問佢點解唔自殺"},{"pid":"8af1a940bc37d13b50b0a84358a8505e741a0bd7","tid":1589743,"uid":14494,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T11:58:41.000Z","msg":"岩呀, 乜都要文宣<br />\n就算前線手足唔講, 企係記者身邊既人記得解釋番<br />\n以武制暴係咁, 拆牆爆站都係"},{"pid":"0a5ff282df2f7c62db15087aa808eb9a7ce5306a","tid":1589743,"uid":71335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-2